<h2>7/8. YouTube Video / Shorts Views (requires API key)</h2>
<p class="small">To fetch view counts you need a YouTube Data API key. Add it into the code variable <code>YOUTUBE_API_KEY</code> and enable "YouTube Data API v3" in Google Cloud Console.</p>
